blue cod
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Parapercis colias</i>, fam Mugiloididae (occas. listed as Parapercidae or Pinguipedidae): a popular coastal food fish, bluish, greenish or brownish-grey, restricted to NZ.; coal fish, pakirikiri, rawaru, rock cod
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
